    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "### Example 2: \"Space Escape Mission\"\r\n\r\n**Narrative:** The player is an astronaut trying to escape from a malfunctioning space station. They must solve problems related to oxygen levels, repair systems, and decide whom to trust among crewmates.\r\n\r\n**Key Features:**\r\n- Three decision points\r\n- Uses if-else conditions for branching paths\r\n- Interactive elements like countdowns or simple puzzles",
    "ai_tutor_available": "false",
    "submittable": "false",
